author: Diana-Horsens
title: Diana-Horsens
text:
I do recommend to everyone. Nesides that is a good deal, the range of products is awesome. I already have 2 orders from them, one woth cosmetics and one with home stuff. The orders were put late in the evening, Fridays. Saturday morning got already the mail from the orders being pakked and sent. Monday morning, were in Horsens for me in perfect shape.
Love them!
